item.title: Stunning Beautiful City Of Khulna
item.description: khulna is the third largest city of Bangladesh after Dhaka city and Chittagong City. Khulna is very old city and third largest economy area of Bangladesh out of others division. Khulna is most popular worldwide for largest mangrove forest specially for grand Royal Bengal tigers, the beautiful Sundari ðŸŒ´ tress and stunning beauty of green mangrove forests.
